abbreviation.notes: Uses epic DEP field DEP_ID, if it exists. If not, use the Kyruus field location_id instead. If neither of these fields exist, fallback to None.

isHidden.notes: If the department exists in Epic DEP, mark isHidden as false. If the department is not in Epic's DEP, then check Kyruus's searchable field; if it is true, then mark isHidden as False for the department. If neither of these conditions are true, fallback to marking the department as True for isHidden.
